# Transcoded responsive photo variants (~17 MB). Production serves
# these from the public `<project>-assets` GCS bucket (uploaded by
# `cli assets upload`), so the `COPY web web` builder step must not
# bundle them into the image. The rest of `web/public` (Bootstrap,
# brand SVGs) still ships, and the runtime `COPY /src/web/public`
# carries the thinned tree.
web/public/img/
